  <td bgcolor="#99CCCC">CDC had just completed a cooperative study with a number of gay community
health clinics--a multiyear, multisite study of hepatitis B:
    <ul>
<li>
risk factors</li>

<li>
patterns of sexual transmission</li>

<li>
prevalence among homosexual men</li>
</ul>
Researchers found hepatitis B to be significantly associated with (among
other factors):
<ul>
<li>
number of sexual partners</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>
sexual practices that involved anal contact</li>
</ul></td>
