<li>
name <b>AIDS [Acquired Immune Deficiency]</b> first used</li>

<ul>
<li>
defined as disease at least moderately predictive of a defect in cell-mediated
immunity, occurring in a person with no known cause for diminished resistance
to that disease</li>
</ul>
</ul></td>
